parameters.name: 10日常パート・放課後等落ち着いたシーン

parameters: Butcher Shop Owner: "Phew~ You really saved me!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "I thought it was all over when that monster took
over my shop."
Butcher Shop Owner: "Thank you, brave young lady! No... Pony-Celes!"
Pony-Celes: "No, no, protecting everyone in town - that's my mission!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "A mission, huh? Just like a true hero! You're so
reliable!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "That's right! Then, my mission is to make sure
everyone gets to eat delicious croquettes and regain their energy!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "How about it? Want to take home some of Butcher
Masa's special beef croquettes as a souvenir? They'll blow away all
the fatigue of today!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "Of course, there's no charge. It's my way of
saying thanks for the help!"

Pony-Celes: "I love Butcher Masa's croquettes! Well then, I'll gladly
accept..."
Pony-Celes: "Please give me four beef croquettes!!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "Hahaha, four of them! You sure can eat. Is Pony-
Celes a big eater? Ahahahaha!"
Pony-Celes: "Tch, that's not it! Half of them are for a friend, geez!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "Oh, is that so? My apologies, ahahaha. Eat to
your heart's content!"

Butcher Shop Owner: "I'll put in eight then! Don't worry about it just
because you're a big eater, young lady!"

Pony-Celes: "No, that's not what I mean! I don't eat that much,
really----!"
Shall we remove the fence and go inside?
